{"tid":1848444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣封得咁好都有8單 香港真係等死","createTime":"2020-01-28T12:51:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T13:15:21.000Z","uid":59818,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7e7900a6716840101864bd778536c3f891de559e","tid":1848444,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:51:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/481065478629613/posts/2666945160041623/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F481065478629613%2Fposts%2F2666945160041623%2F&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGQfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=008dd876\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/481065478629613/posts/2666945160041623/</a><br />\n【#武漢肺炎】#快訊 8例確診！台灣出現首例本土感染案例<br />\n<br />\n「武漢肺炎」疫情升溫。疾管署於晚上8點再度緊急召開記者會，宣布台灣國內出現第一位密集追蹤者遭到感染，為中部50多歲男性，為先前確診第5例境外移入個案之同住家人，於1月26日出現咳嗽症狀就醫，經檢驗於今(28)日確診，研判為家戶感染，並未出國。晚間一例連同下午宣布的兩例新增（來台旅遊之武漢民眾），目前台灣總共有8例確診。<br />\n<br />\n晚間8點記者會中，衛福部部長陳時中親自說明，由於目前受到部分追蹤監測者並未做好居家隔離，仍在外遊走，研判監控需要升級，因此明（29）日開始要對目前國內受到監測追蹤的2000多人進行電子監控升級，每人配備一支手機，不但可以進行視訊訪視、手機也可定位掌握其移動範圍。<br />\n<br />\n目前接受14日密切監控與居家隔離者包括和確診病例有過接觸的、以及有湖北旅遊史的人。<br />\n指揮中心統計，截至1月28日下午4時，國內嚴重特殊傳染性肺炎新增52例通報個案，截至目前共通報578名嚴重特殊傳染性肺炎個案，檢驗結果為8名確診、321名排除、75名初驗陰性、其餘仍待檢驗；另有9例為之前通報不明原因肺炎，均已排除。<br />\n<br />\n關於武漢肺炎，你該知道的事：<br />\n<br />\n►揪出「武漢肺炎」元兇 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/38JEck0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F38JEck0&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGQfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=a5ab614e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/38JEck0</a><br />\n►中國衛健委：「武漢肺炎」潛伏期也具傳染力 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2uGq24g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2uGq24g&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGQfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=bb1be103\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2uGq24g</a><br />\n►除了「囤口罩」，還有10大防疫重點 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2O4T6JL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2O4T6JL&d=rcEdfnhTqGmqsB%2B6X%2FYCGQfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=6fcb9326\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2O4T6JL</a>"},{"pid":"b79241cfa61e4ce252f5d2a7ee4b5bd6db68e8c8","tid":1848444,"uid":253978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:52:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/l43pOY4LQouhi2i1s3/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fl43pOY4LQouhi2i1s3%2Fgiphy.gif&h=7c016c7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"392a734c943a11db78bd6e2e51d3907fea9b427a","tid":1848444,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:52:30.000Z","msg":"支那一向防不勝防<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f2046e0924395d8b007b2e237cb2535d82d9c6","tid":1848444,"uid":132352,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:57:56.000Z","msg":"香港有好多初步確診個d都冇報  一定唔止8單"},{"pid":"36bc263de6315e05f2de7f3aedb0e923703aaf7f","tid":1848444,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:58:54.000Z","msg":"仲要已經有本地感染"},{"pid":"150d096f815e3fdeda23f3f989c18c734b26890b","tid":1848444,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:59:03.000Z","msg":"入去推10下！<br />\n<br />\n「正視聽！」拆解林鄭記招政策幾乎零作用！全力籌備1.29 2.03大三罷！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848456</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a6b6b624bf47c40f9a02d713a91efe769c7a2c9f","tid":1848444,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T12:59:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">除咗醫護之外<br />\n垃圾政府都推緊社福界去死</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">學校停 康文設施都停<br />\n啲人就湧晒去唔停嘅中心<br />\n社區爆發岌岌可危<br />\n<br />\n<ins>要求立即停止所有非緊急服務</ins></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845195</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img s